OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry
OL,6,Fevening with plenty of sunshine,
OL,7,Fperhaps still cloudy around East
OL,8,FLothian. Cloud filling in during the
OL,9,Fnight with some light rain around the
OL,10,Fwest by dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FCloudy with some isolated
OL,13,Flight showers in place, some brighter
OL,14,Fspells developing later in the day,
OL,15,Fespecially for Dumfries and Galloway,
OL,16,Fwinds remaining light.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
