OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA
OL,6,Fbright start on Monday but a few
OL,7,Fshowers developing and cloudy at
OL,8,Ftimes. Remaining settled on Tuesday
OL,9,Fand Wednesday with bright or sunny
OL,10,Fspells and light winds.
